---
title: Down Home Steak ’n’ Potatoes Garlic Herb Butter, Mixed Greens & Creamy Mustard Sauce
description: Remember speed dial? Speed dating? Speed skating? Well get ready for speed dinner–from box to plate in 15 minutes (or less!), and it’s no slouch. Lean, old-school, beefy steak is quick seared, then finished with garlic-herb butter and drizzled with a mustard cream sauce. It’s served with a side of buttery steamed potatoes, and a fresh mixed green salad. A real homey, robust, and fuss-free meal idea for any weeknight.
